00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:07.640
Number Four: mirror body language.

00:04:07.720 --> 00:04:13.020
55% of attraction communication is made through body language,

00:04:13.020 --> 00:04:14.740
and one of the most subtle,

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:20.560
yet most effective methods of flirting with someone is to mirror their actions.

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:24.760
This is because we unconsciously copy those we're attracted to

00:04:24.760 --> 00:04:28.120
as a sign we're interested in what they're saying.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:32.620
Mirroring someone demonstrates that we have good communication skills

00:04:32.660 --> 00:04:37.060
